{"tid":37834,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家睇到呢兩張圖有咩感受？","createTime":"2016-12-13T14:31:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T14:37:36.000Z","uid":31225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b4491b582dc972971b3f300c84b6245b5c444eae","tid":37834,"uid":31225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T14:31:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/13/222858_3f08557cdc10273d22b9352ff0df7b2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F13%2F222858_3f08557cdc10273d22b9352ff0df7b2f.jpg&h=fb538a1a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C1Lag5Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC1Lag5Q.jpg&h=d8ab881d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我真係唔知講咩好。我覺得係呢個地方要生存都好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每個月既人工扣埋家用月月清，究竟我番工係為左咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284b0e40fe10b8a84f38c6e7a50280c83d053e88","tid":37834,"uid":31225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T14:35:38.000Z","msg":"點解民望越低，反而越有得加人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f2dca2a7bc40e46f33b6505ffc13dc6811e099","tid":37834,"uid":6745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T14:35:45.000Z","msg":"狗官"},{"pid":"0fd1b577ffdccc369e9e7787fb30e425e0164f32","tid":37834,"uid":31225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T14:37:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>狗官</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個社會點解可以咁反常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hk